 Website Propaganda
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 Set approximately 10 years after the events of the original Bioshock, the
 halls of Rapture once again echo with sins of the past. Along the Atlantic
 coastline, a monster has been snatching little girls and bringing them back
 to the undersea city of Rapture. You are the very first Big Daddy as you
 travel through the decrepit and beautiful fallen city, chasing an unseen foe
 in search of answers and your own survival.
 
    
 Install Notes
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 1. Extract RARs
 2. Copy Bioshock2Launcher.exe to this folder
    ...BioShock 2SPBuildsBinaries
    ...BioShock 2MPBuildsBinaries
 3. enjoy!
